name: rna_predict
tagline: Python package for RNA tertiary structure prediction
body:
# rna_predict

The ``rna_predict`` Python package models a complete workflow for RNA tertiary
structure prediction using the secondary structure information as well as
optional, additional constraints.

See the Github project page for more information.
The documentation can be found [here](docs/).
